NAME

DateTime::Locale::haw_US - Locale data examples for the Hawaiian United States (haw-US) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Hawaiian United States locale.

Date Formats

Full

   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = Poʻalima, 22 Kekemapa 1995
